{"tid":1172174,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓流】孝琳捲校園暴力爭議 受害者：當時只希望自己出交通意外","createTime":"2019-05-26T08:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T10:36:41.000Z","uid":143093,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a3949cc8d9bba5247f96d9b560cd9f4b50dbb366","tid":1172174,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7EKy9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7EKy9p.jpg&h=f6547bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日不少韓星被爆是校園暴力者，繼韓國人氣獨立樂隊Jannabi的成員尹英賢被爆高中時欺凌同學而主動退團後，今日韓媒就爆料指韓國女團SISTAR前成員孝琳同樣屬校園暴力加害者。<br />\n根據網民A某在網上留言表示，自己和孝琳屬同一間中學，並持續受到其霸凌。A某指孝琳會經常搶走其衣服和現金等，而A某受欺凌原因竟因為她男友名字與孝琳的男友一樣，同時表示：「整整3年，我堅持了下來，連我自己都覺得神奇我居然沒有自殺。在回家的路上我會成為孝琳洩憤的對象，當時只希望自己遇上交通意外。」A某在過去15年都依然擺脫不了這段回憶，每次在電視上見到孝琳就會轉台，去年A某曾鼓起勇氣給孝琳私下傳訊息，希望她道歉，但卻沒有得到回覆。<br />\n孝琳所屬事務所表示要確認消息，其後表示：「因孝琳本人對15年前的記憶已經不太清晰，目前正在確認事情是否屬實。 」同時表示會聯絡受害人，希望能盡快解決事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190526/59642593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190526%2F59642593&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18Baf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=3b1dee70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190526%2F59642593&h=31d37396\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190526/59642593</a><br />\n堅定流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08aff03c3f8f65160e79d3bb6368d8648d8c24b0","tid":1172174,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:00:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7a4bf1105f20cffcfd255b76b7f840c3190f29","tid":1172174,"uid